items.raw_text:
26-1100
City Clerk report and City Attorney report and draft Ordinance relative to calling a Primary Nominating Election on Tuesday, June 2, 2026, and a General Municipal Election on Tuesday, November 3, 2026, in the City of Los Angeles and the Los Angeles Unified School District, and authorizing their consolidation with the State Primary and General Elections to be held on the same dates; and a Resolution requesting authority to consolidate the City of Los Angeles Primary Nominating Election and General Municipal Election with the State Primary and General Elections to be held on June 2, 2026 and November 3, 2026, respectively.
Fiscal Impact Statement:
Yes
Community Impact Statement:
None submitted.
Report from City Clerk dated 11-06-25
Attachment to Report dated 11-06-25 - Resolution
Report from City Attorney dated 11-12-25
Attachment to Report dated 11-12-25 - Draft Ordinance
